title: 'Really bad
column5: The major problem is with the buckle, it will get scratches easily and will then start to rust. I have barely used it for 15 days and the scratches on it has already started to make it look ugly. It isn't even worth 289₹, you can get it for around 150₹ on other sites and even cheaper if you buy it locally.

title: 'Dont purchase it
rating: if you wanna use it for a long duration.'
column5: The product is good in appearance and texture. But if you want to use it for a regular purpose never purchase it. The lock is good, but the belt material of low quality and get torned within a weeks time. The belt gets struck with in the lock as the belt easily get damaged. So don't purchase it, if you want to use it for a 6 months duration.
